Title: The icy embrace of the atlantic
Narrative:
I can't recall if I have ever seen an OCEAN...maybe I saw the Indian Ocean when I was little but seeing the atlantic ocean here in this little corner of nowhere , happiness has soared ! 
Hello from me and AppuEsthose who might appear to be on holiday, but definitely isn't ...workaholic much.
